mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record and Record Report", "As I See It, by Bob Osgood", "Welcome to the Lucky 13th", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Looking Into the Future", "Style Series: Contras Made Simple", "Ladies on the Square: Perky Party Punch Ideas", "Round the Outside Ring", "Sets in Order Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Chuck Raley", "Paging the Roundancers: Frank & Char Buchan", and "Experimental Lab: Swing Star Thru".
